"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tkd1665702792997.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tkd1665702792997.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tkd1665702792997.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tkd1665702792997\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Resource Browser (Project Editor)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Create new main development objects (modeled entities, modeled components, components, and libraries) and add new and existing objects and files to the Project.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tkd1665702792997__section_w3406ab1b5b1_w3407ab1b5_w3408ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tkd1665702792997__section_xpc_qzd_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d167285e56\">Tabs</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"tkd1665702792997__ul_k2z_qzd_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tkd1665702792997__li_d2447e1_d2448e1_d2449e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Templates</span>—lists templates for\n          creating main development objects in this project. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tkd1665702792997__li_d2450e1_d2451e1_d2452e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Model</span>—lists existing modeled\n          components that can be used to create components that inherit definitions from the modeled\n          component. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tkd1665702792997__li_d2453e1_d2454e1_d2455e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Objects</span>—lists existing\n          development objects that can be added to the current project. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tkd1665702792997__li_d2456e1_d2457e1_d2458e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tables</span>—facility for creating\n          modeled entities by loading definitions from an existing database. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tkd1665702792997__section_jsk_tzd_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d167285e85\">How to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"tkd1665702792997__ul_hcp_5zd_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tkd1665702792997__li_d2459e1_d2460e1_d2461e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"flj1690357335479.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/flj1690357335479.html\" title=\"You can select templates, modeled objects, and code snippets in the Resource Browser and add them to current object. You can drag and drop objects, or use the context menu.\">Add Objects from the Resource Browser</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tkd1665702792997__li_d2462e1_d2463e1_d2464e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yed1704964703330.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yed1704964703330.html\" title=\"The number of objects available for selection in the Resource Browser may be very large, so you can filter the content in a variety of ways, depending on context.\">Filter and Search for Objects in Resource Browser</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tkd1665702792997__li_d2465e1_d2466e1_d2467e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"abg1665702623914.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/abg1665702623914.html\" title=\"For some databases, you can import the data dictionary definitions of an existing database into the application model using the Load Definitions facility, which is provided in Project Editor, in the Tables tab of the Resource Browser.\">Import Data Definitions From a DBMS</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532392\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532392\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Resource Browser (Project Editor) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Resource Browser (Project Editor) Create new main development objects (modeled entities, modeled components, components, and libraries) and add new and existing objects and files to the Project. Tabs Templates —lists templates for creating main development objects in this project. Model —lists existing modeled components that can be used to create components that inherit definitions from the modeled component. Objects —lists existing development objects that can be added to the current project. Tables —facility for creating modeled entities by loading definitions from an existing database. How to Add Objects from the Resource Browser Filter and Search for Objects in Resource Browser Import Data Definitions From a DBMS Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}